In addition, many brands have launched new car models recently and it is expected that the new cars will significantly increase sales volume.
Amidst the trend of consumption upgrading, people pay more attention to meeting the demands for “the spirit”, and the ratio of the service consumption in culture, education, and other aspects is increasing.
