The World Tourism Day, designated on September 27 annually, revolves around the theme of "Tourism and Jobs: a better future for all" this year, and for this, the Macao Government Tourism Office (MGTO) has organized a series of activities to celebrate with residents and visitors, including greeting the Lucky Tourists and the traditional Tray Race.
